            <forecast-period index="2" start-time-local="2026-05-06T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-05-07T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-05-05T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-05-06T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. High chance of showers, most likely in the late morning and afternoon. Winds west to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h turning south to southwesterly 25 to 40 km/h in the afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to between 8 and 11 with daytime temperatures reaching around 20.</text>
